OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly sunny in the south and
OL,6,Fbecoming warm by the afternoon. A
OL,7,Flittle more cloud further north and
OL,8,Fbreezier and cooler here with an
OL,9,Fisolated light shower possible,
OL,10,Fespecially over the higher ground.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry night will then follow
OL,13,Fwith winds falling light for all. A
OL,14,Fmix of some cloud and clear spells.
OL,15,FTurning rather chilly under prolonged
OL,16,Fclear skies.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FSunday will be a fine day with
OL,19,Flight winds and a mix of fair weather
OL,20,Fcloud and sunny spells. Feeling a
OL,21,Flittle warmer for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
